ObexFTP Virtual FileSystem for Midnight Commander


WHAT IS IT
   Manipulate a cell phone's filesystem in Midnight Commander using obexftp
binary.


WHAT'S NEW
Version 1.4.0 (2013-11-16)
   Get charset from the environment.

Version 1.3.2 (2013-11-11)
   Documented the fact that the script can be put in
$HOME/[.local/share/].mc/extfs.d.

Version 1.3.0 (2010-05-09)
   USB transport.

Version 1.2.0 (2004-09-27)
   Fixed a major bug with blocked read from a pipe. Many thanks to
Marius Konitzer <m.konitzer@gmx.de> for reporting the bug. Now I use files
instead of pipes.
   More tests during parsing of a transport file.


